## üìä TraceQL Query Examples

Use these in the Explore view:

```sql
# All traces
{}

# By service name
{resource.service.name="my-app"}

# Slow requests (>100ms)
{duration > 100ms}

# HTTP errors
{span.http.status_code >= 400}

# Specific operation
{name = "GET /api/users"}
```

## üü¢ Node.js Example

**tracing.js** (loaded via `--require`):
```javascript
const { NodeSDK } = require('@opentelemetry/sdk-node');
const { getNodeAutoInstrumentations } = require(
  '@opentelemetry/auto-instrumentations-node');
const { OTLPTraceExporter } = require(
  '@opentelemetry/exporter-trace-otlp-grpc');
const grpc = require('@grpc/grpc-js');

const sdk = new NodeSDK({
  traceExporter: new OTLPTraceExporter({
    url: 'http://oib-alloy-telemetry:4317',
    credentials: grpc.credentials.createInsecure(),
  }),
  instrumentations: [getNodeAutoInstrumentations()],
});
sdk.start();
```

**package.json**:
```json
"scripts": {
  "start": "node --require ./tracing.js app.js"
}
```

üìÅ See `examples/node-express` for complete example
